If you don't need a reference to the `CountDownLatch` param, you could do:
```java
AmplifyWebSocketListener(CountDownLatch latch) {
    this.latch = latch;
}

AmplifyWebSocketListener() {
    this(new CountDownLatch(1));
}
```

